[
  {
    "startTime": 0.5,
    "endTime": 1.96,
    "text": "Well, you know I'm a fan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1.96,
    "endTime": 2.61,
    "text": "I love you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.61,
    "endTime": 5.52,
    "text": "And you were here last year."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.52,
    "endTime": 7.4399999999999995,
    "text": "And look at what's happened."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.44,
    "endTime": 8.52,
    "text": "I mean, your life."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.52,
    "endTime": 9.93,
    "text": "And you were so shy then."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.93,
    "endTime": 11.16,
    "text": "I think you're still shy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.16,
    "endTime": 15.42,
    "text": "But you've probably grown a whole lot this year, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.42,
    "endTime": 16.379,
    "text": "I would hope so."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.379,
    "endTime": 18.6,
    "text": "I feel like I can talk to you more now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.6,
    "endTime": 20.28,
    "text": "Yeah?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.28,
    "endTime": 22.5,
    "text": "Because you you-- even when I watch you interviewed--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.5,
    "endTime": 25.23,
    "text": "because I watched all of the US Open."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.23,
    "endTime": 25.87,
    "text": "I just love it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.87,
    "endTime": 28.3,
    "text": "And I watched that match when you beat Coco."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.3,
    "endTime": 30.39,
    "text": "And it was really tough because people--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.39,
    "endTime": 33.143,
    "text": "you know, she's brand new and she did so well at Wimbledon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.143,
    "endTime": 34.56,
    "text": "And everybody was like Coco, Coco."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.56,
    "endTime": 36.21,
    "text": "And she plays you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.21,
    "endTime": 39.2,
    "text": "And it was just amazing how you handled that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.2,
    "endTime": 40.260000000000005,
    "text": "It was so beautiful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.26,
    "endTime": 42.129999999999995,
    "text": "And I texted right away."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.13,
    "endTime": 42.870000000000005,
    "text": "And just--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.87,
    "endTime": 45.791999999999994,
    "text": "[APPLAUSE]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.98,
    "endTime": 51.73,
    "text": "Did you look at her understanding?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.73,
    "endTime": 52.779999999999994,
    "text": "Is that why you did that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.78,
    "endTime": 55.06,
    "text": "What that would have felt like for you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.06,
    "endTime": 56.56,
    "text": "Yeah, I mean, for me, I think it was"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.56,
    "endTime": 59.300000000000004,
    "text": "a combination of everything."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.3,
    "endTime": 61.147999999999996,
    "text": "And I know that a lot of people came"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.148,
    "endTime": 62.440000000000005,
    "text": "and watched that match for her."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.44,
    "endTime": 65.86,
    "text": "And normally, people don't watch the press conferences after."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.86,
    "endTime": 68.89,
    "text": "So I wanted her to get the chance to address everybody."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.89,
    "endTime": 71.26,
    "text": "Yeah, that was really sweet of you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.26,
    "endTime": 72.76,
    "text": "I was watching when you--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.76,
    "endTime": 74.23,
    "text": "who did you play after that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.23,
    "endTime": 75.34,
    "text": "Who beat you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.34,
    "endTime": 77.05,
    "text": "What was her name?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.05,
    "endTime": 77.8,
    "text": "What was her name?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.8,
    "endTime": 79.75999999999999,
    "text": "No, I'm just kidding."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.76,
    "endTime": 80.92,
    "text": "Her name's Bencic."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.92,
    "endTime": 81.49,
    "text": "That's right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.49,
    "endTime": 82.27,
    "text": "That's right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.27,
    "endTime": 83.92,
    "text": "OK, but when you were walking out"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.92,
    "endTime": 86.48,
    "text": "being interviewed, before you walked out, they said,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.48,
    "endTime": 88.48,
    "text": "what are you going to do to change up your game?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.48,
    "endTime": 90.4,
    "text": "And you said, I don't really think about that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.4,
    "endTime": 91.31800000000001,
    "text": "Actually, I'm lying."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.318,
    "endTime": 93.61,
    "text": "Like, it was so funny because you just caught yourself."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.61,
    "endTime": 96.73,
    "text": "And you're so honest the way you speak."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.73,
    "endTime": 100.15,
    "text": "Is that something that you feel like you're"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.15,
    "endTime": 101.74000000000001,
    "text": "better at just kind of expressing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.74,
    "endTime": 106.39,
    "text": "exactly how you feel instead of just kind of being quiet?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.39,
    "endTime": 109.94,
    "text": "I mean, you just said I'm quiet, though."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.94,
    "endTime": 116.38499999999999,
    "text": "No, I mean, I like just being straightforward and honest."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.385,
    "endTime": 118.51,
    "text": "So, yeah, that usually gets me in a lot of trouble,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.51,
    "endTime": 119.80000000000001,
    "text": "like with you, you know?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.8,
    "endTime": 121.6,
    "text": "Why does that get you in trouble?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.6,
    "endTime": 124.85,
    "text": "Because, you know, last time I was here,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.85,
    "endTime": 126.41,
    "text": "you just did me dirty."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.41,
    "endTime": 126.91,
    "text": "So--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.91,
    "endTime": 129.60999999999999,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.61,
    "endTime": 133.19000000000003,
    "text": "All I did was try to fulfill a fantasy of yours."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.19,
    "endTime": 133.69,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.69,
    "endTime": 134.38,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.38,
    "endTime": 137.68,
    "text": "You said that Michael B. Jordan was your crush."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.68,
    "endTime": 141.79000000000002,
    "text": "So I reached out to him, and then he texted."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.79,
    "endTime": 146.26,
    "text": "And I think I put out there what he said."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.26,
    "endTime": 147.917,
    "text": "And, I mean, he loves you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.917,
    "endTime": 149.5,
    "text": "And it was just unfortunate because he"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.5,
    "endTime": 153.13,
    "text": "didn't get back to me in time while you were still here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.13,
    "endTime": 155.71,
    "text": "But he really was a huge fan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.71,
    "endTime": 157.51000000000002,
    "text": "Why is that dirty?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.51,
    "endTime": 159.64,
    "text": "Man, you say it so nicely."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.64,
    "endTime": 160.83999999999997,
    "text": "I can't even say anything."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.84,
    "endTime": 163.54,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.54,
    "endTime": 166.56799999999998,
    "text": "What would you say if I said he's here now?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.568,
    "endTime": 168.36,
    "text": "You guys are getting excited for no reason."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.36,
    "endTime": 170.26000000000002,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.26,
    "endTime": 176.5,
    "text": "First of all, OK, I would to be calm because I'm a calm person."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.5,
    "endTime": 177.642,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.642,
    "endTime": 178.6,
    "text": "All right, she's right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.6,
    "endTime": 179.183,
    "text": "He's not here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.183,
    "endTime": 180.81,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.81,
    "endTime": 181.6,
    "text": "But Brad Pitt is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.6,
    "endTime": 182.79999999999998,
    "text": "Did you meet Brad?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.8,
    "endTime": 183.61,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.61,
    "endTime": 184.72000000000003,
    "text": "Well, you should."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.72,
    "endTime": 187.45,
    "text": "Well, I was hiding so that I didn't have to bump into him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.45,
    "endTime": 188.35,
    "text": "Oh, really?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.35,
    "endTime": 188.887,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.887,
    "endTime": 189.97,
    "text": "Isn't he adorable, though?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.97,
    "endTime": 191.16,
    "text": "Don't you want to meet him?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.16,
    "endTime": 192.38,
    "text": "Do you want to meet Brad?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.38,
    "endTime": 192.88,
    "text": "I have--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.88,
    "endTime": 195.44,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.44,
    "endTime": 196.43,
    "text": "I've met Brad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.43,
    "endTime": 197.55,
    "text": "OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.55,
    "endTime": 198.8,
    "text": "All right, we'll take a break."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.8,
    "endTime": 200.86,
    "text": "And we'll see if you want to meet Brad or not."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.86,
    "endTime": 201.887,
    "text": "We'll take a break."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.887,
    "endTime": 203.72,
    "text": "I'm saying, I was asking if she gets nervous"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.72,
    "endTime": 205.85,
    "text": "before matches because that's a lot of people."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.85,
    "endTime": 208.09799999999998,
    "text": "And I guess you get used to people watching you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.098,
    "endTime": 208.64000000000001,
    "text": "all the time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.64,
    "endTime": 212.33999999999997,
    "text": "But that is a lot of pressure of people watching you play,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.34,
    "endTime": 213.38,
    "text": "right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.38,
    "endTime": 214.391,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.391,
    "endTime": 216.73499999999999,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.735,
    "endTime": 218.36,
    "text": "You really have come out of your shell."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.36,
    "endTime": 220.73000000000002,
    "text": "It's great."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.73,
    "endTime": 222.86999999999998,
    "text": "So Brad is back getting interviewed by Jaden."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.87,
    "endTime": 225.71,
    "text": "So you'll meet Brad when you go back there because maybe he'll"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.71,
    "endTime": 229.07000000000002,
    "text": "take over as your crush, unless you are continuing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.07,
    "endTime": 231.51999999999998,
    "text": "Do you still have a crush on Michael B. Jordan?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.52,
    "endTime": 233.996,
    "text": "I have a crush on you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.996,
    "endTime": 235.77800000000002,
    "text": "No, I was just kidding."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 235.778,
    "endTime": 237.32,
    "text": "What do you mean you're just kidding?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.9,
    "endTime": 244.34,
    "text": "So Michael B. Jordan on Twitter invited you to go"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 244.34,
    "endTime": 245.612,
    "text": "see \"Creed 2.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.612,
    "endTime": 247.07,
    "text": "And you didn't even respond to him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.07,
    "endTime": 248.63,
    "text": "And then you didn't show up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.63,
    "endTime": 249.65,
    "text": "How is that possible?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.65,
    "endTime": 250.97,
    "text": "I try to hook things up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.97,
    "endTime": 253.60999999999999,
    "text": "I get it all set up for you, and then you don't even"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 253.61,
    "endTime": 256.279,
    "text": "respond or go to the premiere."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.279,
    "endTime": 258.709,
    "text": "Why wouldn't you do that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 258.709,
    "endTime": 260.213,
    "text": "You're never going to get a man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 260.213,
    "endTime": 261.572,
    "text": "Whoa!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.572,
    "endTime": 262.84,
    "text": "Whoa."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.84,
    "endTime": 264.59,
    "text": "You gotta like-- When somebody puts it out"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264.59,
    "endTime": 266.71299999999997,
    "text": "there for you, take it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 266.713,
    "endTime": 267.63,
    "text": "Is that how you do it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 267.63,
    "endTime": 268.94,
    "text": "Let me tell you how to get a man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 268.94,
    "endTime": 269.44,
    "text": "OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.44,
    "endTime": 271.83,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.83,
    "endTime": 274.98499999999996,
    "text": "Let me be the one to teach you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274.985,
    "endTime": 276.36,
    "text": "All right, so here's what we did."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.36,
    "endTime": 277.652,
    "text": "I didn't want to embarrass you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 277.652,
    "endTime": 278.66999999999996,
    "text": "He's not here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.67,
    "endTime": 280.08000000000004,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 280.08,
    "endTime": 282.41999999999996,
    "text": "So what we did is--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 282.42,
    "endTime": 283.59000000000003,
    "text": "this is outside."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.59,
    "endTime": 285.28999999999996,
    "text": "This is on--Barham"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 285.29,
    "endTime": 286.36,
    "text": "Olive."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 286.36,
    "endTime": 287.22,
    "text": "Olive?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 287.22,
    "endTime": 292.122,
    "text": "All right, let's just take a look at the banner outside now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 292.122,
    "endTime": 294.612,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 294.612,
    "endTime": 298.098,
    "text": "[APPLAUSE]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 307.25,
    "endTime": 308.8,
    "text": "You just really did that, huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 308.8,
    "endTime": 310.08,
    "text": "Uh-huh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 310.08,
    "endTime": 310.93,
    "text": "Yup, I did that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 310.93,
    "endTime": 311.74,
    "text": "OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 311.74,
    "endTime": 313.38,
    "text": "All right."
  }
]